Nginx RTMP Server (nrs)

This is simple builder for nginx with rtmp module, from UPG.GR-MEDIA-SERVER project...

nginx ver: mainline 1.11.3
nginx-rtmp module: git master


USAGE: 
-clone, edit nginx.sh to your needs & run: 
  git clone https://github.com/beginho/nrs.git
  
-quick run w/o clonning UBUNTU: 
  curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/beginho/nrs/master/nginx_ubuntu.sh | sudo bash -

-quick run w/o clonning CENTOS: 
  curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/beginho/nrs/master/nginx_centos.sh | sudo bash -
  
Tested with Ubuntu 14.04 Server . . .

